Test_View_2.@DataWarehouse.sqlEditor.query:
SELECT main.SourceLedger,
	main.CompanyCode,
	main.FiscalYear,
	main.AccountingDocument,
	main.LedgerGLLineItem,
	CompCode.FiscalYearVariant,
	main.AmountInCompanyCodeCurrency,
	main.CompanyCodeCurrency
FROM I_GLACCOUNTLINEITEMRAWDATA AS main
	INNER JOIN I_COMPANYCODE AS CompCode ON main.CompanyCode = CompCode.CompanyCode
WHERE main.FiscalYear = :FISCAL_YEAR
